{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "mmi-website-collection-2024",
    "name": "MMI Website API Collection",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Museum Musik Indonesia (MMI) Website.\n\n## Important Notes\n- This is a Laravel + Inertia.js application, most routes return HTML/Inertia responses\n- For POST requests, you may need CSRF token handling\n- Set `base_url` variable in Postman environment\n\n## CSRF Token Setup (for Web Routes)\n1. First call GET {{base_url}}/sanctum/csrf-cookie (if using Sanctum)\n2. Or manually get XSRF-TOKEN from browser cookies\n3. Add header: X-XSRF-TOKEN: [token_value]",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "midtrans_server_key",
      "value": "YOUR_MIDTRANS_SERVER_KEY",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
